{"tid":558458,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"我認為依個世界必須要存在無自信嘅人","createTime":"2018-02-12T09:50:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-12T12:29:49.000Z","uid":64694,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1e605c8e817c2f5d694f753409659468aebc1a1b","tid":558458,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T09:50:27.000Z","msg":"唔知大家有無聽過二元論呢?<br />\n<br />\n讀大學嘅時候讀過一個通識科, 其中一個概念叫陰陽, 即係話依個世界嘅任何事物都會有兩邊, 互相對立又互補不足, 相互依存, 例如天地, 上下, 肥絲好鍾意嘅左右, 光暗之類, 每一邊都不能太強, 否則就會物極必反, 失去平衡<br />\n<br />\n所以有自信嘅人同無自信嘅人都必須要存在, 試想想如果全世界嘅人都過份有自信會出現咩事?<br />\n個個都想show off自己, 但明明有啲人嘅長處根本唔係咁, 例如有自信嘅毒撚, 夾硬要show off自己只會帶來反效果, 令人尷尬之餘更令自己出醜, 咁又何苦呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"356ee7447520c41b9412a60994b03401104be4b1","tid":558458,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T11:39:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a3cf4a98ca770388f932184b48f65ffff5b5c3c","tid":558458,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T11:43:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d256425f784388e98b6a8af5d40642d9799be97","tid":558458,"uid":29370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T11:44:39.000Z","msg":"咁樓主係邊樣？"},{"pid":"e553d631a6f27a70c5d0e0883b89a02da6b342ad","tid":558458,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d256425f784388e98b6a8af5d40642d9799be97","tid":558458,"uid":29370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T11:44:39.000Z","msg":"咁樓主係邊樣？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T11:46:42.000Z","msg":"無自信嘅毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"805a99cf43008f498804b55c6d209859e9cdb7a8","tid":558458,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T12:29:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji